title: 628. Looking Back at First QB Selected in Last 11 Drafts
itunes:title: 628. Looking Back at First QB Selected in Last 11 Drafts
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a special new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys look at the first quarterback selected in the last 11 NFL Drafts, while also determining which quarterback ended up being the best in each of those drafts (3:50). After that, the pair react to the news of the Carolina Panthers firing general manager Marty Hurney and discuss if it's a good opening (20:04). Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
